#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:2
#: e937a9bff61743afb253e901e34edf7c
msgid "Geomechanics: Drucker-Prager strip footing"
msgstr "岩土力学:Drucker-Prager 条形基础"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:4
#: bf49a13e8f14442dba3df4f7f399f250
msgid ""
"This example combines two geomechanics building blocks into one nonlinear "
"boundary-value problem: TensorMesh's public Drucker-Prager material model "
"and the elastic strip-footing setup.  A rectangular soil block is loaded by "
"a centered strip footing, the footing pressure is ramped in load steps, and "
"the per-quadrature Drucker-Prager history is committed after each converged "
"step."
msgstr ""
"本示例把两个岩土力学构件结合成一个非线性边值问题:TensorMesh 的公共 Drucker-Prager "
"材料模型和弹性条形基础设置。一个矩形土块由中心条形基础加载,基础压力按载荷步逐级增加,每个收敛步后提交逐求积点的 Drucker-Prager 历史。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:10
#: 53e11ce523ad410fbc3a28dbcad4477b
msgid ""
"The constitutive model is the built-in "
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.DruckerPragerPlasticity` assembler, configured "
"with a :class:`~tensormesh.material.FrictionalMaterial`. TensorMesh keeps "
"the internal solid-mechanics convention stress tension-positive. For "
"geomechanics reporting, settlement is shown positive downward,"
msgstr ""
"本构模型是内置的 :class:`~tensormesh.assemble.DruckerPragerPlasticity` 装配器,配以 "
":class:`~tensormesh.material.FrictionalMaterial`\\ 。TensorMesh "
"内部固体力学约定保持应力拉为正。为岩土力学报告,沉降以向下为正显示,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:16
#: bebdcc640985406a94c7d5040b2cb906
msgid "s = -u_y."
msgstr "s = -u_y."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:20
#: d8d0e267508647878363f69545628c3b
msgid "This is a compact educational example, not a foundation-design method."
msgstr "这是一个紧凑的教学示例,而非基础设计方法。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:23
#: ce8d7bb8176f4876bb4a1ae88a6607bd
msgid "Problem"
msgstr "问题"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:25
#: 6655c8ea594448a0a54f9a0a68c88e94
msgid ""
"The model is a two-dimensional plane-strain-style soil block with unit out-"
"of-plane thickness.  The constitutive model is small-strain, associated "
"Drucker-Prager plasticity with linear isotropic hardening, written "
"internally with the tension-positive yield function"
msgstr ""
"该模型是二维平面应变式土块,面外厚度为单位 1。本构模型是带线性各向同性硬化的小应变、关联 Drucker-Prager "
"塑性,内部以拉为正的屈服函数写成"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:30
#: a93adecc2ac8406298a72e45c40629f8
msgid ""
"f(\\sigma, \\alpha) = q + \\eta I_1 - (k + H\\alpha) \\le 0,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"I_1 = \\mathrm{tr}(\\sigma),\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"q = \\sqrt{\\tfrac{3}{2}\\,s:s}."
msgstr ""
"f(\\sigma, \\alpha) = q + \\eta I_1 - (k + H\\alpha) \\le 0,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"I_1 = \\mathrm{tr}(\\sigma),\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"q = \\sqrt{\\tfrac{3}{2}\\,s:s}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:39
#: 7e89535f38f84ce7a680206eb94a88c0
msgid "Boundary conditions"
msgstr "边界条件"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:41
#: e309b253e7dd47ddbabb009e3252bd27
msgid "The example reuses the elastic footing roller setup:"
msgstr "本示例复用弹性基础的滚动支座设置:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:43
#: 52de5441ed0747e08bc304c3730edc8a
msgid "bottom boundary: vertical displacement fixed, ``u_y = 0``;"
msgstr "底部边界:竖向位移固定,``u_y = 0``;"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:44
#: d60efb4606e045d59c31fa1c37484b94
msgid "left and right boundaries: horizontal displacement fixed, ``u_x = 0``;"
msgstr "左右边界:水平位移固定,``u_x = 0``;"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:45
#: 4e0d1b372d46405397040c69d3073fe9
msgid "top boundary: free except for the loaded footing patch."
msgstr "顶部边界:除受载基础块外自由。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:47
#: ad46815e86e94ddcb58af782cbd43ebd
msgid ""
"The footing pressure is lumped over the top-surface nodes inside the footing"
" patch."
msgstr "基础压力被集总到基础块内的顶面节点上。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:51
#: 4f9f9e52d20c4d8181bfc2b881d81c23
msgid "Solver"
msgstr "求解器"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:53
#: af549ea5c00646fba8d99b0a024b6dd0
msgid ""
"Because the problem is now path-dependent, it is solved by nonlinear energy "
"minimization with load stepping.  At each load step the total potential "
"energy ``internal - external`` is minimized over the free displacement DOFs "
"with L-BFGS.  The example follows the same per-quadrature history lifecycle "
"as the ``drucker_prager_triaxial`` example:"
msgstr ""
"由于问题现在是路径相关的,它通过带载荷步进的非线性能量最小化来求解。在每个载荷步,用 L-BFGS 在自由位移自由度上最小化总势能 ``internal"
" - external``\\ 。该示例遵循与 ``drucker_prager_triaxial`` 示例相同的逐求积点历史生命周期:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:59
#: 74e46a468ee34af9b3fa5caf0a4805d3
msgid ""
"per-quadrature history variables are stored in ``self.history[etype]``;"
msgstr "逐求积点历史变量存储在 ``self.history[etype]`` 中;"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:60
#: d5e07b4b2c86468fb0a5755304e8b26f
msgid ""
"previous-step ``eps_p`` and ``alpha`` are passed through ``element_data``;"
msgstr "上一步的 ``eps_p`` 和 ``alpha`` 通过 ``element_data`` 传入;"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:61
#: c29ebe5447bf420e99e3f7dd28f7062c
msgid ""
"``update_state(u)`` is called after each converged load step under "
"``torch.no_grad()``."
msgstr "``update_state(u)`` 在 ``torch.no_grad()`` 下、每个收敛载荷步后调用。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:65
#: 436ea77d564f4e449f3515dc536b8a05
msgid "Sanity checks"
msgstr "合理性检验"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:67
#: 75d9508e9090423a998c34a4661cd8c5
msgid ""
"The script reports the final footing settlement, the maximum settlement, the"
" maximum and mean committed plastic history, and the plastic centroid."
msgstr "脚本报告最终基础沉降、最大沉降、提交的塑性历史的最大值与均值,以及塑性质心。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:70
#: 7bb9fcb7d5c44bd4a76400ac3ae59061
msgid ""
"The associated test checks that the footing settles downward, that the "
"committed plastic history and settlement grow monotonically with load, that "
"the plastic zone localizes under the footing, that a low-load / high-"
"cohesion case stays essentially elastic and matches the elastic footing "
"settlement, and that a higher-cohesion soil develops less plasticity."
msgstr ""
"相应的测试检查:基础向下沉降、提交的塑性历史与沉降随载荷单调增长、塑性区在基础下方局部化、低载荷/高黏聚力情形基本保持弹性并与弹性基础沉降吻合,以及黏聚力更高的土体发展出更少的塑性。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:76
#: d8e512b1710043099ca8d66fc53dacf6
msgid ""
"Drucker-Prager strip-footing settlement, plastic history, and load-"
"settlement curve"
msgstr "Drucker-Prager 条形基础的沉降、塑性历史与载荷-沉降曲线"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:80
#: 3d26878a301c402d85f5b714ad0950f3
msgid ""
"Output of ``drucker_prager_footing.py``. The left panel shows the deformed "
"soil mesh colored by settlement ``-u_y``. The middle panel shows the "
"committed Drucker-Prager plastic history variable, which develops beneath "
"the footing. The right panel shows the load-settlement curve, including "
"nonlinear growth as plasticity accumulates. Deformations are exaggerated for"
" visibility."
msgstr ""
"``drucker_prager_footing.py`` 的输出。左面板显示按沉降 ``-u_y`` 着色的变形土网格。中面板显示提交的 "
"Drucker-Prager 塑性历史变量,它在基础下方发展。右面板显示载荷-沉降曲线,包括塑性累积时的非线性增长。为便于观察,变形被放大。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:88
#: 99f2ce562d844f42ba5af8629fcf7211
msgid "Running it"
msgstr "运行它"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:95
#: 7eace047f7e549e7868e94beca962eae
msgid "For a fast numerical-only run without writing the plot:"
msgstr "若只想快速做纯数值运行而不写出图:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:102
#: c1c309640cfe4de48675951ef8b4e1ec
msgid "Core implementation"
msgstr "核心实现"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:104
#: dd044452ae1b476598e10c78ba25df5a
msgid ""
"The load-stepped nonlinear solver is the heart of the example.  It uses the "
"built-in :class:`~tensormesh.assemble.DruckerPragerPlasticity` assembler's "
"``energy``, ``element_data_from_history`` and ``update_state`` methods."
msgstr ""
"载荷步进的非线性求解器是本示例的核心。它使用内置 "
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.DruckerPragerPlasticity` 装配器的 ``energy``\\ 、\\ "
"``element_data_from_history`` 和 ``update_state`` 方法。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:113
#: 4fc6fb1c639b454ca9073bbc29f2ef15
msgid "What's next"
msgstr "下一步"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_footing.rst:115
#: 8407dfc4201e4c42b3e9d34d6a7f03dc
msgid ""
"A natural follow-up would be to add non-associated flow and pore-pressure "
"coupling to the public Drucker-Prager model, or to reuse this footing "
"geometry with other built-in geomechanics materials as they are added."
msgstr ""
"一个自然的后续是为公共 Drucker-Prager 模型加入非关联流动和孔压耦合,或随着更多内置岩土力学材料的加入,用此基础几何复用它们。"
